OL,7,FTwo years ago, I was there as the most
OL,8,Frecent conflict in Sudan began, and
OL,9,Fwesterners were urgently evacuated
OL,10,Ffrom its capital city ` Khartoum.
OL,12,FIt was soon after that Sudan
OL,13,Fdisappeared from the attention of the
OL,14,Fworld.
