OL,7,FThe UN says half the population, 25
OL,8,Fmillion people, are facing acute
OL,9,Fhunger.
OL,11,FThey say hunger has tripled since war
OL,12,Fbroke out, and it is now catastrophic
OL,13,Fin ten out of 18 states.
OL,15,FFamine has been declared in not just
OL,16,Fone, but ten areas of a country eight
OL,17,Ftimes the size of the UK, according to
OL,18,Fthe organisation, and the number of
OL,19,Fareas hit is growing, as 17 are now on
OL,20,Fthe brink of famine.
