OL,7,FEmergency doctor Dr Javid Abdelmoneim
OL,8,Frecounted to ITV News the desperate
OL,9,Fsituation he witnessed in Sudan
OL,11,FDr Javid Abdelmoneim is an emergency
OL,12,Fmedicine specialist for Medecins Sans
OL,13,FFrontieres, and has worked in conflict
OL,14,Fzones for the past 15 years.
OL,16,FSpeaking to ITV News after his return
OL,17,Ffrom Sudan, Dr Abdelmoneim said:
OL,18,F"There's already been famine declared,
OL,19,Fimagine how much worse it's going to
OL,20,Fget.
