OL,7,FNine million Sudanese people have been
OL,8,Fdriven from their homes across the
OL,9,Fcountry in just the past 24 months,
OL,10,Fequal to the entire total population
OL,11,Fof London.
OL,13,FMore than half of those 9 million are
OL,14,Fchildren, meaning one child is being
OL,15,Fdisplaced every ten seconds.
OL,17,FWe spoke to displaced 15-year-old
OL,18,FNahid Ahmed Abdukar, from the Abuja
OL,19,FCamp in Al-Fasher.
