OL,7,F"Before the war, I lived a peaceful
OL,8,Flife filled with dreams and
OL,9,Faspirations," she said.
OL,11,F"I was preparing for my high school
OL,12,Fexams when the conflict erupted,
OL,13,Fforcing schools to close. The war
OL,14,Fshattered my morale and spirit," she
OL,15,Fadded.
OL,17,FUNICEF told us Nahid's experience is
OL,18,Fall too familiar, as no matter where
OL,19,Fyou go in Sudan, you find waves and
OL,20,Fwaves of displaced populations.
