OL,7,FLargest global child protection crisis
OL,9,FWhen charities speak of the child
OL,10,Fcrisis, they mean sexual violence
OL,11,Fagainst children.
OL,13,FThis is a very difficult subject to
OL,14,Fget direct evidence on in any society,
OL,15,Flet alone one where access to victims
OL,16,Fis extremely difficult and where all
OL,17,Fsides to the conflict make it
OL,18,Fdifficult.
