OL,7,FThis all comes as the government today
OL,8,Fannounced a #120 million food and aid
OL,9,Fpackage at a conference in London.
OL,11,FOpening the summit, Foreign Secretary
OL,12,FDavid Lammy said it was "morally
OL,13,Fwrong" that "many have given up on
OL,14,FSudan".
OL,16,FMr Lammy said "with over four million
OL,17,Frefugees having fled the country and
OL,18,Finstability spreading far beyond
OL,19,FSudan's borders, it's also
OL,20,Fstrategically wrong to forget Sudan."
