OL,7,F"And that's why, as foreign secretary,
OL,8,FI refuse to turn away. I felt a duty
OL,9,Fto confront this war's horrors head
OL,10,Fon."
OL,12,FThe summit, co-hosted by the UK
OL,13,Falongside the African Union, the
OL,14,FEuropean Union, France and Germany,
OL,15,Fwas attended by representatives from
OL,16,Fcountries including South Sudan, Saudi
OL,17,FArabia and the US.
