OL,7,FMr Lammy told the conference that
OL,8,F"patient diplomacy" was needed to
OL,9,F"relieve the suffering and to end this
OL,10,Fawful war."
OL,12,F"We cannot be back here one year from
OL,13,Fnow having the same discussion. So
OL,14,Ftoday let's show them and the world
OL,15,Fthat we've not given up on them. We've
OL,16,Fnot given up on Sudan."
