OL,7,FThe new #120 million funding aims to
OL,8,Freach more than 600,000 people, with
OL,9,Fthe money going towards supplying
OL,10,Fpulses, oils, salts and cereals to the
OL,11,Fvulnerable.
OL,13,FIt will also help provide emergency
OL,14,Fsupport to survivors of sexual
OL,15,Fviolence.
OL,17,FIt follows a separate #113 million aid
OL,18,Fpackage announced last November,
OL,19,Fbefore the Government decision to cut
OL,20,FUK development spending by 2027.
